{"blogid": "125068226", "writerAge": "码龄1年", "writerBlogNum": "8", "writerCollect": "15", "writerComment": "3", "writerFan": "1", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "86", "writerName": "摸鱼中...", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_125068226.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "129768", "writerRankWeekly": "989350", "writerThumb": "2", "writerVisitNum": "6938", "blog_read_count": "2307", "blog_time": "于 2022-05-31 16:41:07 发布", "blog_title": "Visual Studio 2022的下载安装及使用", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\">Visual Studio 2022的下载与安装。</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\">网页链接：<a href=\"https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/zh-hans/vs/\" title=\"Visual Studio 2022 IDE - 适用于软件开发人员的编程工具\">Visual Studio 2022 IDE - 适用于软件开发人员的编程工具</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"323\" src=\"image\\8bd4e486e9054c16b2ec4aa6607c23f4.png\" width=\"504\"/></p>\n<p>1.安装开发所需的工具和组件捆绑包</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"294\" src=\"image\\5e894387778a47fb98e7b9e67566753d.png\" width=\"544\"/></p>\n<p> 2.安装后，在电脑菜单找到Visual Studio Installer 打开，然后点击修改。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"132\" src=\"image\\360cdfa127844986b78733795adb5ecf.png\" width=\"545\"/></p>\n<p> 3.进入工作负荷页面后，勾选需要安装的捆绑。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"314\" src=\"image\\9921f911aeed47709b00f12f664eebda.png\" width=\"562\"/></p>\n<p> 然后点击关闭就可以了。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Visual Studio 2022的使用</p>\n<p>在桌面双击打开Visual Studio 2022 </p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"410\" src=\"image\\ba350cabf52f475a917ebf4a7e423ad3.jpeg\" width=\"553\"/></p>\n<p> 1.创建新项目</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"381\" src=\"image\\7e88806914114769a4d650fa950d1583.jpeg\" width=\"558\"/></p>\n<p> 2.配置新项目</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"414\" src=\"image\\206a42d28f9e490588f8dc0082898ec6.jpeg\" width=\"557\"/></p>\n<p> 3.创建成功后就可以写代码了，下图是执行程序的结果。</p>\n<p class=\"img-center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"278\" src=\"image\\61ccb6b06d5b4659bfd0f761c8dc9440.jpeg\" width=\"563\"/></p>\n<p> 以上就是我想要分享Visual Studio 2022的下载安装及使用的相关内容。</p>\n<p>VS的几个常用快捷键：</p>\n<p>1.Ctrl + K，Ctrl + C   注释选定内容</p>\n<p>2.Ctrl + K，Ctrl + U   取消注释选定内容</p>\n<p>3.Ctrl + K，Ctrl + /   切换行注释</p>\n<p>4.Ctrl + Shift + /   切换块注释</p>\n<p>5.Ctrl + D  向下复制当前行</p>\n<p>6.F5  调试运行</p>\n<p>7.Shift + F5 停止调试</p>\n<p>大概就是这个样子的了。如果有什么不懂的可在下方评论！</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>"}